          <li><strong>Side-by-side comparison:</strong> The <a href="/compare/" class="text-indigo-600 dark:text-indigo-400 hover:underline">comparison tool</a> lets you evaluate 2+ metros simultaneously across cost, safety, jobs, schools, childcare cost, and environment.</li>
